{"tid":1993293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小心五毛有組織歪曲民調報告去攪散內會抗爭","createTime":"2020-04-28T16:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T00:47:39.000Z","uid":26770,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4099575ccb54bb04871876a7246059e15bff3dfd","tid":1993293,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:13:40.000Z","msg":"公民黨支持度跌有好多原因, 因為公民黨過去把捍衛法官當成捍衛法治<br />\n 這是香港法律界的普遍問題<br />\n因西方文明國的保守派法官都無香港黨委法官的狂搬龍門惡行<br />\n<br />\n<ins>當一連串司法迫害出現, 以往企係香港法庭一方的公民黨當然奶野</ins><br />\n而唔係五毛講的群眾不喜歡拉布<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家見對家通過黨媒放風屈飯民想散水咪呢個玩法</span>"},{"pid":"84023c0deedca8120dff86287a30eb3b4345bfe1","tid":1993293,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:22:31.000Z","msg":"第一式放風老屈飯民<br />\n見所有奶共報紙同時聲稱有風就知係西環駱公公的局<br />\n大陸人從來做野就係無美感同核突<br />\n姐係昔日深圳一堆大紅字banner叫人遵守計劃生育<br />\n<br />\n大陸人做野永遠係有一種柒味, 請港奸做野都無撚用, 因為最後決定點下筆係大陸佬<br />\n<br />\n第二式就係搵分化撚開post話民意反拉布<br />\n但份調查根本唔係涉獵呢類野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">見到呢d撚樣拉post就ok,唔好去反駁</span><br />\n絕大部分users 只睇頭一頁,你反駁姐係推post</span>"},{"pid":"5fe739d6df2fb1c33f28cc316b0b5763c3c9321e","tid":1993293,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:29:01.000Z","msg":"我認為飯民唔似跪左<br />\n<br />\n對家出左呢類古怪騎呢招咪證明係後台都擺唔平飯民<br />\n最緊要企得夠實, 唔好理班棄城派/投降派講咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一定要清算班畜牲強姦警, 要呢班人全家成為賤藉賤種</span>"},{"pid":"c60563e708ecd6572c3765ebcc5c0403229b8296","tid":1993293,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fe739d6df2fb1c33f28cc316b0b5763c3c9321e","tid":1993293,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:29:01.000Z","msg":"我認為飯民唔似跪左<br />\n<br />\n對家出左呢類古怪騎呢招咪證明係後台都擺唔平飯民<br />\n最緊要企得夠實, 唔好理班棄城派/投降派講咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一定要清算班畜牲強姦警, 要呢班人全家成為賤藉賤種</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffbb5344188c288b2757bdcdad1665bd64f82239","tid":1993293,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:39:30.000Z","msg":"其實最好破解方法就係俾同路人信心<br />\n泛民只要用行動證明再加說明<br />\n白頭佬今日係教科書小會議屌奶共派： 唔洗你教我主持會議<br />\n已經好好，同路人既信心都大好多<br />\n當然，我地都要保持警惕，要監察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家我地無讓步機會，讓步與否都會俾支共打壓<br />\n重要說話講三次讓步與否都會俾支共打壓！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">讓步與否都會俾支共打壓</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">讓步與否都會俾支共打壓</span><br />\n大家只能共舟共濟、破釜沉舟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9110349bcda79f0b5575cf413dcfeba1f0e353c","tid":1993293,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1kJ7Ufw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1kJ7Ufw.gif&h=ee5bd90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新登記選民截止日期：2020年5月2日</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk2020.vote/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote%2F&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImKnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=77a13522\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk2020.vote/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jL0uupX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjL0uupX.gif&h=b8ede5bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><code>圖片來源：#35432 速食保濟丸 @LIHKG</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1990059\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1990059</a></div><br />\n<br />\n